{"video_id": "Sqqw2JDxTfI", "title": "Daily Evening Bhagavatam Discourse | HH Stoka Krishna Swami | SB 1.12.18| 14-08-2022", "speaker": "HH Stoka Krishna Swami", "youtube_url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Sqqw2JDxTfI", "duration": 950, "segments": [{"start": 0.0, "end": 15.040000000000001, "text": " ओम ग्यानति मिरान्धस्या ग्यानान्जनिषलाकया चक्षरण्मीलितं येनतस्मै श्री गुरवे नमः नमाः ओमिष्णु पादाया कृष्ण प्रिष्ठाय भूतले श्रीमते भक्ति वेदान्त स्वामिन्नितिनामिने"}, {"start": 15.040000000000001, "end": 30.64, "text": " नमस्ते सारस्वते देवे गौरवाणी प्रचारिने निर्विशेशा शून्यवादी पास्चात्यदेशतारिने जाय श्री कृष्ण चैतन्या प्रभूनित्यानन्दा श्री अद्वाईतगडाधर श्रीवासाधी गौरभक्त वृन्दा"}, {"start": 30.64, "end": 49.28, "text": " Hare Krishna, Hare Krishna, Krishna Krishna, Hare Hare, Hare Rama, Hare Rama, Rama Rama, Hare Hare, Om Namo Bhagavate Vasudevaya, Narayanam Namaskritya, Naram Chai Vanarottamam, Devim Saraswatim Vyasam Tato Jayam Udi Rayet."}, {"start": 49.28, "end": 59.86, "text": " In this session we will be discussing from the 18th verse of the 12th chapter of the first canto of Srimad Bhagavatam. The topic of this chapter is the birth of Emperor Pariksit."}, {"start": 59.86, "end": 77.74000000000001, "text": " Shri Rajovacha Apyesha Vamsyaan Rajarsheen Punya Shlokan Mahatmanaha Anuvartitha Svithyashasa Sadhuvadena Sattamaha"}, {"start": 77.74000000000001, "end": 79.26, "text": " This is the birth of Emperor Pariksit."}, {"start": 79.26, "end": 85.72, "text": " This is a word spoken by King Yudhishthira to the Brahmins in response to what they said. Now he is asking a question."}, {"start": 86.72, "end": 89.16000000000001, "text": " The good King Yudhishthira inquired,"}, {"start": 90.02000000000001, "end": 105.4, "text": " O great souls, will he become as saintly a king, as pious in his very name, and as famous and glorified in his achievements as others who appeared in this great royal family?"}, {"start": 107.4, "end": 109.24000000000001, "text": " So this verse is a question."}, {"start": 109.26, "end": 111.26, "text": " This is a question by King Yudhishthira to the Brahmins."}, {"start": 113.26, "end": 117.26, "text": " So Shri La Pravapara explains in the purport to this verse."}, {"start": 118.26, "end": 124.26, "text": " The forefathers of King Yudhishthira were all great saintly kings."}, {"start": 125.26, "end": 128.26, "text": " Rajarsheen. The term used is Rajarsheen."}, {"start": 129.26, "end": 136.26, "text": " They are Raja, they are kings, but they are also Rishi, they are saintly, saintly kings."}, {"start": 137.26, "end": 138.26, "text": " It's a rare combination."}, {"start": 139.26, "end": 147.26, "text": " And all of them are pious and glorified by their great achievements."}, {"start": 151.26, "end": 160.26, "text": " They are all pious, because they strictly follow the scriptures, and they are glorified by their great achievements."}, {"start": 163.26, "end": 168.26, "text": " Their achievements are noteworthy, even for kings."}, {"start": 169.26, "end": 171.26, "text": " They are future generations."}, {"start": 173.26, "end": 182.26, "text": " So they are all recorded in the Vedic scriptures."}, {"start": 183.26, "end": 190.26, "text": " And they are glorified, and their example is cited again and again and again."}, {"start": 191.26, "end": 198.26, "text": " They are the ideal for everyone else in the society."}, {"start": 199.26, "end": 201.26, "text": " Even in future."}, {"start": 203.26, "end": 214.26, "text": " So their example is a timeless example."}, {"start": 215.26, "end": 221.26, "text": " They don't go out of relevance,"}, {"start": 221.26, "end": 227.26, "text": " because there may be some very ancient examples of a different time,"}, {"start": 227.26, "end": 230.26, "text": " of a different era."}, {"start": 231.26, "end": 241.26, "text": " Because the nature of a person"}, {"start": 242.26, "end": 245.26, "text": " is essentially spiritual."}, {"start": 246.26, "end": 254.26, "text": " And that spiritual nature doesn't change with the change of time,"}, {"start": 254.26000000000002, "end": 261.26, "text": " change of era, change of yuga, change of place, change of circumstances."}, {"start": 261.26, "end": 264.26, "text": " The spiritual nature does not change."}, {"start": 266.26, "end": 268.26, "text": " So further Srila Prabhupada says,"}, {"start": 268.26, "end": 272.26, "text": " they were all saints on the royal throne."}, {"start": 273.26, "end": 274.26, "text": " They are sitting on the royal throne."}, {"start": 274.26, "end": 275.26, "text": " They are ruling."}, {"start": 276.26, "end": 277.26, "text": " They are powerful."}, {"start": 278.26, "end": 283.26, "text": " And they can be very, very tough in dealing with miscreants."}, {"start": 284.26, "end": 287.26, "text": " But they are saints."}, {"start": 288.26, "end": 290.26, "text": " They have all the qualities of a sadhu,"}, {"start": 291.26, "end": 292.26, "text": " of a saintly person."}, {"start": 294.26, "end": 295.26, "text": " And therefore,"}, {"start": 296.26, "end": 298.26, "text": " as a result of such people ruling,"}, {"start": 299.26, "end": 301.26, "text": " what is being described here, please hear."}, {"start": 302.26, "end": 305.26, "text": " Therefore, all the members of the state,"}, {"start": 306.26, "end": 307.26, "text": " all the citizens,"}, {"start": 308.26, "end": 309.26, "text": " were happy,"}, {"start": 310.26, "end": 311.26, "text": " pious,"}, {"start": 312.26, "end": 313.26, "text": " well-behaved,"}, {"start": 313.26, "end": 314.26, "text": " prosperous,"}, {"start": 314.26, "end": 316.26, "text": " and spiritually enlightened."}, {"start": 317.26, "end": 319.26, "text": " Five things Prabhupada says"}, {"start": 319.26, "end": 321.26, "text": " about the citizens"}, {"start": 321.26, "end": 324.26, "text": " who are under the care of"}, {"start": 325.26, "end": 328.26, "text": " great saintly kings, Rajarshis."}, {"start": 328.26, "end": 331.26, "text": " First of all, people are happy."}, {"start": 332.26, "end": 334.26, "text": " This is a primary"}, {"start": 336.26, "end": 338.26, "text": " characteristic"}, {"start": 338.26, "end": 341.26, "text": " of a saintly person ruling"}, {"start": 341.26, "end": 342.26, "text": " a kingdom."}, {"start": 343.26, "end": 344.26, "text": " Or a state,"}, {"start": 344.26, "end": 345.26, "text": " or a province,"}, {"start": 345.26, "end": 346.26, "text": " or a country,"}, {"start": 346.26, "end": 347.26, "text": " or even the whole world."}, {"start": 348.26, "end": 350.26, "text": " All the people are happy."}, {"start": 351.26, "end": 352.26, "text": " Why?"}, {"start": 352.26, "end": 358.26, "text": " Because of his perfect rule,"}, {"start": 358.26, "end": 363.26, "text": " there is plenty of supply of all necessities"}, {"start": 364.26, "end": 366.26, "text": " by Mother Earth."}, {"start": 368.26, "end": 369.26, "text": " Plenty of supply."}, {"start": 370.26, "end": 372.26, "text": " So there is no scarcity of anything."}, {"start": 372.26, "end": 374.26, "text": " For anyone."}, {"start": 375.26, "end": 377.26, "text": " So naturally people will be happy."}, {"start": 379.26, "end": 381.26, "text": " And then people are also,"}, {"start": 381.26, "end": 382.26, "text": " they are pious."}, {"start": 383.26, "end": 386.26, "text": " Because the saintly kings enforce"}, {"start": 387.26, "end": 389.26, "text": " the scriptural"}, {"start": 391.26, "end": 392.26, "text": " directions"}, {"start": 393.26, "end": 394.26, "text": " to be followed by everybody"}, {"start": 394.26, "end": 395.26, "text": " for their own good."}, {"start": 396.26, "end": 397.26, "text": " For the good of the whole country,"}, {"start": 397.26, "end": 399.26, "text": " for the good of the whole world."}, {"start": 400.26, "end": 401.26, "text": " So there are no"}, {"start": 401.26, "end": 403.26, "text": " clashes"}, {"start": 404.26, "end": 405.26, "text": " between different"}, {"start": 406.26, "end": 407.26, "text": " sections of people"}, {"start": 407.26, "end": 408.26, "text": " in the society."}, {"start": 410.26, "end": 412.26, "text": " People can live in harmony,"}, {"start": 413.26, "end": 414.26, "text": " peacefully."}, {"start": 416.26, "end": 418.26, "text": " And because of the prosperity,"}, {"start": 418.26, "end": 419.26, "text": " they are all happy."}, {"start": 419.26, "end": 421.26, "text": " Everyone is"}, {"start": 422.26, "end": 424.26, "text": " having everything they require."}, {"start": 425.26, "end": 426.26, "text": " And"}, {"start": 427.26, "end": 429.26, "text": " people are well behaved."}, {"start": 429.26, "end": 432.26, "text": " They are well behaved because"}, {"start": 432.26, "end": 434.26, "text": " they are all"}, {"start": 435.26, "end": 436.26, "text": " trained up"}, {"start": 436.26, "end": 438.26, "text": " to follow their respective"}, {"start": 441.26, "end": 442.26, "text": " duties,"}, {"start": 442.26, "end": 444.26, "text": " to perform their respective duties."}, {"start": 445.26, "end": 447.26, "text": " Everyone is trained up"}, {"start": 448.26, "end": 449.26, "text": " in the Vedic culture."}, {"start": 450.26, "end": 453.26, "text": " The whole society is divided into four"}, {"start": 454.26, "end": 456.26, "text": " social classes"}, {"start": 456.26, "end": 458.26, "text": " and four spiritual classes."}, {"start": 459.26, "end": 461.26, "text": " So the four social classes"}, {"start": 461.26, "end": 462.26, "text": " are the Brahmanas,"}, {"start": 462.26, "end": 463.26, "text": " Kshatriyas,"}, {"start": 463.26, "end": 464.26, "text": " Vaishyas,"}, {"start": 464.26, "end": 465.26, "text": " and Shudras."}, {"start": 465.26, "end": 467.26, "text": " So they have a certain nature,"}, {"start": 467.26, "end": 468.26, "text": " acquired nature."}, {"start": 468.26, "end": 469.26, "text": " Accordingly,"}, {"start": 469.26, "end": 470.26, "text": " they are trained"}, {"start": 470.26, "end": 472.26, "text": " and they are engaged"}, {"start": 472.26, "end": 474.26, "text": " in occupational duties."}, {"start": 474.26, "end": 476.26, "text": " So everyone contributes"}, {"start": 476.26, "end": 478.26, "text": " to the society positively."}, {"start": 480.26, "end": 482.26, "text": " And the others acknowledge,"}, {"start": 484.26, "end": 485.26, "text": " I may be"}, {"start": 485.26, "end": 490.26, "text": " inclined to work like a Brahmana."}, {"start": 490.26, "end": 492.26, "text": " So I give my contribution"}, {"start": 492.26, "end": 494.26, "text": " to the society"}, {"start": 494.26, "end": 496.26, "text": " in terms of giving guidance"}, {"start": 496.26, "end": 497.26, "text": " to the people,"}, {"start": 497.26, "end": 499.26, "text": " in terms of"}, {"start": 500.26, "end": 502.26, "text": " educating them,"}, {"start": 503.26, "end": 504.26, "text": " in terms of teaching them"}, {"start": 504.26, "end": 506.26, "text": " how to worship God,"}, {"start": 506.26, "end": 508.26, "text": " in terms of"}, {"start": 508.26, "end": 510.26, "text": " giving them guidance"}, {"start": 510.26, "end": 511.26, "text": " about"}, {"start": 511.26, "end": 514.26, "text": " their own responsibilities, duties."}, {"start": 515.26, "end": 516.26, "text": " Like that."}, {"start": 517.26, "end": 518.26, "text": " So,"}, {"start": 518.26, "end": 519.26, "text": " I do my duty"}, {"start": 520.26, "end": 521.26, "text": " and the"}, {"start": 521.26, "end": 522.26, "text": " Kshatriyas,"}, {"start": 522.26, "end": 523.26, "text": " they do their duty"}, {"start": 523.26, "end": 524.26, "text": " giving protection"}, {"start": 524.26, "end": 525.26, "text": " to the citizens,"}, {"start": 525.26, "end": 527.26, "text": " collecting taxes,"}, {"start": 527.26, "end": 529.26, "text": " spending the tax money"}, {"start": 529.26, "end": 531.26, "text": " for the public welfare."}, {"start": 533.26, "end": 534.26, "text": " Then the Vaishyas,"}, {"start": 534.26, "end": 535.26, "text": " they do"}, {"start": 535.26, "end": 537.26, "text": " economic development"}, {"start": 537.26, "end": 538.26, "text": " by"}, {"start": 538.26, "end": 539.26, "text": " trading,"}, {"start": 539.26, "end": 540.26, "text": " commerce,"}, {"start": 541.26, "end": 542.26, "text": " by growing food grains,"}, {"start": 542.26, "end": 544.26, "text": " by giving cow protection,"}, {"start": 545.26, "end": 548.26, "text": " so plenty of milk,"}, {"start": 548.26, "end": 549.26, "text": " milk products,"}, {"start": 549.26, "end": 551.26, "text": " plenty of grains,"}, {"start": 552.26, "end": 554.26, "text": " plenty of minerals,"}, {"start": 554.26, "end": 555.26, "text": " everything."}, {"start": 556.26, "end": 557.26, "text": " The Vaishyas"}, {"start": 557.26, "end": 559.26, "text": " cultivate the land,"}, {"start": 560.26, "end": 563.26, "text": " they engage in business,"}, {"start": 564.26, "end": 567.26, "text": " trading the excess grains"}, {"start": 567.26, "end": 569.26, "text": " or excess silk"}, {"start": 569.26, "end": 570.26, "text": " or excess"}, {"start": 570.26, "end": 571.26, "text": " of"}, {"start": 572.26, "end": 573.26, "text": " metals,"}, {"start": 573.26, "end": 574.26, "text": " minerals,"}, {"start": 574.26, "end": 575.26, "text": " everything."}, {"start": 575.26, "end": 576.26, "text": " So,"}, {"start": 576.26, "end": 577.26, "text": " the Vaishyas"}, {"start": 577.26, "end": 578.26, "text": " do their"}, {"start": 578.26, "end": 579.26, "text": " work,"}, {"start": 579.26, "end": 581.26, "text": " they give taxes to the government"}, {"start": 581.26, "end": 583.26, "text": " and the government spends it"}, {"start": 583.26, "end": 584.26, "text": " for public welfare."}, {"start": 584.26, "end": 587.26, "text": " The Shudras are engaged according to their"}, {"start": 587.26, "end": 589.26, "text": " proclivities"}, {"start": 589.26, "end": 591.26, "text": " to do a particular type of"}, {"start": 591.26, "end": 593.26, "text": " menial work"}, {"start": 593.26, "end": 595.26, "text": " because they cannot"}, {"start": 595.26, "end": 598.26, "text": " work as a Vaishya or a Kshatriya or a Brahmana."}, {"start": 598.26, "end": 600.26, "text": " They don't have the necessary"}, {"start": 600.26, "end": 603.26, "text": " intellectual development."}, {"start": 603.26, "end": 604.26, "text": " Their"}, {"start": 604.26, "end": 606.26, "text": " nature is not"}, {"start": 606.26, "end": 607.26, "text": " suited for"}, {"start": 607.26, "end": 610.26, "text": " using their intelligence"}, {"start": 610.26, "end": 611.26, "text": " in a Vaishya way"}, {"start": 611.26, "end": 612.26, "text": " or a Kshatriya way"}, {"start": 612.26, "end": 614.26, "text": " or a Brahmana way."}, {"start": 614.26, "end": 615.26, "text": " So,"}, {"start": 615.26, "end": 617.26, "text": " they just are humble,"}, {"start": 617.26, "end": 621.26, "text": " they do whatever they can do"}, {"start": 621.26, "end": 623.26, "text": " as menial service"}, {"start": 623.26, "end": 624.26, "text": " and"}, {"start": 624.26, "end": 625.26, "text": " even for that"}, {"start": 625.26, "end": 627.26, "text": " they are trained up,"}, {"start": 627.26, "end": 628.26, "text": " even in that menial service"}, {"start": 628.26, "end": 629.26, "text": " they are trained up"}, {"start": 629.26, "end": 630.26, "text": " like carpenters,"}, {"start": 630.26, "end": 632.26, "text": " sculptors,"}, {"start": 632.26, "end": 633.26, "text": " the tillers in the land,"}, {"start": 633.26, "end": 635.26, "text": " or the"}, {"start": 635.26, "end": 637.26, "text": " workers who work in a"}, {"start": 637.26, "end": 639.26, "text": " Goshala"}, {"start": 639.26, "end": 641.26, "text": " or workers who work in the"}, {"start": 641.26, "end": 642.26, "text": " in the"}, {"start": 642.26, "end": 643.26, "text": " government,"}, {"start": 643.26, "end": 644.26, "text": " in the"}, {"start": 644.26, "end": 646.26, "text": " military."}, {"start": 646.26, "end": 647.26, "text": " They are trained up"}, {"start": 647.26, "end": 650.26, "text": " to do one specific"}, {"start": 650.26, "end": 652.26, "text": " type of work"}, {"start": 652.26, "end": 653.26, "text": " without"}, {"start": 653.26, "end": 655.26, "text": " trying to use their intelligence"}, {"start": 655.26, "end": 656.26, "text": " in"}, {"start": 656.26, "end": 657.26, "text": " in"}, {"start": 657.26, "end": 658.26, "text": " in"}, {"start": 660.26, "end": 662.26, "text": " understanding some philosophy"}, {"start": 662.26, "end": 663.26, "text": " or some theory,"}, {"start": 663.26, "end": 664.26, "text": " nothing,"}, {"start": 664.26, "end": 666.26, "text": " they just follow."}, {"start": 666.26, "end": 667.26, "text": " That is"}, {"start": 667.26, "end": 669.26, "text": " the level of the Shudra."}, {"start": 669.26, "end": 670.26, "text": " And they are provided with"}, {"start": 670.26, "end": 672.26, "text": " all their needs,"}, {"start": 672.26, "end": 673.26, "text": " they are provided with"}, {"start": 673.26, "end": 674.26, "text": " all their needs"}, {"start": 674.26, "end": 675.26, "text": " by whoever"}, {"start": 675.26, "end": 677.26, "text": " engages them"}, {"start": 677.26, "end": 679.26, "text": " in a respective"}, {"start": 679.26, "end": 680.26, "text": " menial service."}, {"start": 680.26, "end": 681.26, "text": " So,"}, {"start": 681.26, "end": 682.26, "text": " in this way"}, {"start": 682.26, "end": 683.26, "text": " people are"}, {"start": 683.26, "end": 685.26, "text": " well behaved,"}, {"start": 685.26, "end": 687.26, "text": " people are well behaved"}, {"start": 687.26, "end": 689.26, "text": " because they are trained up,"}, {"start": 689.26, "end": 691.26, "text": " they are taught"}, {"start": 691.26, "end": 693.26, "text": " and they have"}, {"start": 693.26, "end": 695.26, "text": " ideals"}, {"start": 695.26, "end": 697.26, "text": " in the society,"}, {"start": 697.26, "end": 698.26, "text": " the saintly persons,"}, {"start": 698.26, "end": 700.26, "text": " the brahmanas,"}, {"start": 700.26, "end": 702.26, "text": " and the"}, {"start": 702.26, "end": 703.26, "text": " rishis,"}, {"start": 703.26, "end": 705.26, "text": " the sages."}, {"start": 705.26, "end": 708.26, "text": " They have ideal examples"}, {"start": 708.26, "end": 709.26, "text": " to follow"}, {"start": 709.26, "end": 711.26, "text": " and people are prosperous"}, {"start": 711.26, "end": 713.26, "text": " because they have plenty of everything."}, {"start": 713.26, "end": 714.26, "text": " There is no scarcity."}, {"start": 714.26, "end": 715.26, "text": " Why?"}, {"start": 715.26, "end": 717.26, "text": " Because Mother Nature provides,"}, {"start": 717.26, "end": 719.26, "text": " Mother Earth provides."}, {"start": 719.26, "end": 721.26, "text": " When there is a saintly person,"}, {"start": 721.26, "end": 723.26, "text": " a saintly king ruling,"}, {"start": 723.26, "end": 724.26, "text": " Mother Earth provides"}, {"start": 724.26, "end": 725.26, "text": " plenty."}, {"start": 725.26, "end": 728.26, "text": " Everybody does their"}, {"start": 728.26, "end": 729.26, "text": " duty,"}, {"start": 729.26, "end": 730.26, "text": " therefore there is"}, {"start": 730.26, "end": 731.26, "text": " yajña,"}, {"start": 731.26, "end": 733.26, "text": " yajña karma samudbhava."}, {"start": 733.26, "end": 735.26, "text": " This is explained in the Bhagavad Gita."}, {"start": 735.26, "end": 736.26, "text": " And,"}, {"start": 736.26, "end": 737.26, "text": " above all,"}, {"start": 737.26, "end": 739.26, "text": " people are"}, {"start": 739.26, "end": 741.26, "text": " spiritually enlightened."}, {"start": 741.26, "end": 744.26, "text": " There is systematic"}, {"start": 744.26, "end": 745.26, "text": " dissemination"}, {"start": 745.26, "end": 746.26, "text": " of"}, {"start": 746.26, "end": 748.26, "text": " spiritual knowledge,"}, {"start": 748.26, "end": 750.26, "text": " which is most essential"}, {"start": 750.26, "end": 753.26, "text": " in human society."}, {"start": 753.26, "end": 754.26, "text": " It cannot be"}, {"start": 754.26, "end": 756.26, "text": " like"}, {"start": 756.26, "end": 757.26, "text": " the government"}, {"start": 757.26, "end": 760.26, "text": " is"}, {"start": 760.26, "end": 762.26, "text": " not concerned with"}, {"start": 762.26, "end": 764.26, "text": " people's"}, {"start": 764.26, "end": 766.26, "text": " spiritual"}, {"start": 766.26, "end": 767.26, "text": " development."}, {"start": 767.26, "end": 768.26, "text": " No."}, {"start": 768.26, "end": 769.26, "text": " Government should be concerned."}, {"start": 769.26, "end": 771.26, "text": " Should be concerned."}, {"start": 771.26, "end": 773.26, "text": " People should understand"}, {"start": 773.26, "end": 775.26, "text": " that they are not the body"}, {"start": 775.26, "end": 777.26, "text": " or at least"}, {"start": 777.26, "end": 779.26, "text": " even if they don't understand philosophically,"}, {"start": 779.26, "end": 782.26, "text": " they should follow"}, {"start": 782.26, "end": 785.26, "text": " the scriptural directions"}, {"start": 785.26, "end": 788.26, "text": " for spiritual advancement"}, {"start": 788.26, "end": 789.26, "text": " by"}, {"start": 789.26, "end": 793.26, "text": " performing some spiritual activity."}, {"start": 793.26, "end": 797.26, "text": " By performing some spiritual activity."}, {"start": 797.26, "end": 798.26, "text": " They should."}, {"start": 798.26, "end": 800.26, "text": " Everyone should."}, {"start": 800.26, "end": 802.26, "text": " That is not a matter of"}, {"start": 802.26, "end": 803.26, "text": " somebody's"}, {"start": 803.26, "end": 805.26, "text": " belief system."}, {"start": 805.26, "end": 808.26, "text": " Spiritual life is not a matter of belief system."}, {"start": 808.26, "end": 810.26, "text": " So,"}, {"start": 810.26, "end": 812.26, "text": " everybody has to understand"}, {"start": 812.26, "end": 814.26, "text": " there is only one supreme Lord."}, {"start": 814.26, "end": 815.26, "text": " And,"}, {"start": 815.26, "end": 816.26, "text": " everyone else"}, {"start": 816.26, "end": 818.26, "text": " other than the supreme Lord"}, {"start": 818.26, "end": 819.26, "text": " is actually"}, {"start": 819.26, "end": 820.26, "text": " under the"}, {"start": 820.26, "end": 821.26, "text": " control"}, {"start": 821.26, "end": 822.26, "text": " of"}, {"start": 822.26, "end": 823.26, "text": " the one and only"}, {"start": 823.26, "end": 824.26, "text": " one supreme Lord."}, {"start": 824.26, "end": 825.26, "text": " There is no question of"}, {"start": 825.26, "end": 826.26, "text": " different religious"}, {"start": 826.26, "end": 827.26, "text": " faiths."}, {"start": 827.26, "end": 828.26, "text": " They say"}, {"start": 828.26, "end": 829.26, "text": " there are different religions"}, {"start": 829.26, "end": 830.26, "text": " in the world"}, {"start": 830.26, "end": 831.26, "text": " because there are"}, {"start": 831.26, "end": 832.26, "text": " different religions."}, {"start": 832.26, "end": 833.26, "text": " There are different religions"}, {"start": 833.26, "end": 834.26, "text": " in the world"}, {"start": 834.26, "end": 835.26, "text": " because there are"}, {"start": 835.26, "end": 836.26, "text": " different religions"}, {"start": 836.26, "end": 837.26, "text": " in the world."}, {"start": 837.26, "end": 838.26, "text": " There are different religions"}, {"start": 838.26, "end": 839.26, "text": " in the world"}, {"start": 839.26, "end": 840.26, "text": " because there are"}, {"start": 840.26, "end": 841.26, "text": " different religious faiths."}, {"start": 841.26, "end": 843.26, "text": " This is a misunderstanding of"}, {"start": 843.26, "end": 844.26, "text": " what is"}, {"start": 844.26, "end": 848.26, "text": " eternal religion."}, {"start": 848.26, "end": 849.26, "text": " It's called"}, {"start": 849.26, "end": 851.26, "text": " Bhagavata Dharma."}, {"start": 851.26, "end": 853.26, "text": " That's what Bhagavatam proclaims."}, {"start": 853.26, "end": 854.26, "text": " And,"}, {"start": 854.26, "end": 855.26, "text": " a king"}, {"start": 855.26, "end": 856.26, "text": " actually"}, {"start": 856.26, "end": 857.26, "text": " enforces"}, {"start": 857.26, "end": 860.26, "text": " Bhagavata Dharma."}, {"start": 860.26, "end": 862.26, "text": " A Rajarshi introduces"}, {"start": 862.26, "end": 863.26, "text": " or enforces"}, {"start": 863.26, "end": 864.26, "text": " Bhagavata Dharma."}, {"start": 864.26, "end": 866.26, "text": " Universal."}, {"start": 866.26, "end": 867.26, "text": " Universal"}, {"start": 867.26, "end": 868.26, "text": " system"}, {"start": 868.26, "end": 869.26, "text": " of"}, {"start": 869.26, "end": 870.26, "text": " Dharma."}, {"start": 870.26, "end": 871.26, "text": " Religion."}, {"start": 871.26, "end": 872.26, "text": " It is not"}, {"start": 872.26, "end": 873.26, "text": " dependent"}, {"start": 873.26, "end": 874.26, "text": " on people's"}, {"start": 874.26, "end": 875.26, "text": " faith."}, {"start": 875.26, "end": 876.26, "text": " No."}, {"start": 876.26, "end": 877.26, "text": " Just like"}, {"start": 877.26, "end": 878.26, "text": " all human beings."}, {"start": 878.26, "end": 879.26, "text": " Why human beings?"}, {"start": 879.26, "end": 880.26, "text": " Even"}, {"start": 880.26, "end": 881.26, "text": " all living"}, {"start": 881.26, "end": 882.26, "text": " creatures."}, {"start": 882.26, "end": 883.26, "text": " They require"}, {"start": 883.26, "end": 884.26, "text": " food."}, {"start": 884.26, "end": 885.26, "text": " And,"}, {"start": 885.26, "end": 886.26, "text": " who provides"}, {"start": 886.26, "end": 887.26, "text": " the food?"}, {"start": 887.26, "end": 888.26, "text": " The supreme Lord."}, {"start": 888.26, "end": 889.26, "text": " The one and only"}, {"start": 889.26, "end": 890.26, "text": " one supreme Lord"}, {"start": 890.26, "end": 891.26, "text": " provides"}, {"start": 891.26, "end": 892.26, "text": " the food"}, {"start": 892.26, "end": 893.26, "text": " for"}, {"start": 893.26, "end": 894.26, "text": " every living"}, {"start": 894.26, "end": 895.26, "text": " being."}, {"start": 895.26, "end": 896.26, "text": " So,"}, {"start": 896.26, "end": 897.26, "text": " this is"}, {"start": 897.26, "end": 898.26, "text": " universal"}, {"start": 898.26, "end": 899.26, "text": " Dharma."}, {"start": 899.26, "end": 900.26, "text": " Universal"}, {"start": 900.26, "end": 901.26, "text": " Dharma."}, {"start": 901.26, "end": 902.26, "text": " So,"}, {"start": 902.26, "end": 903.26, "text": " this way"}, {"start": 903.26, "end": 904.26, "text": " the"}, {"start": 904.26, "end": 905.26, "text": " Rajarshi"}, {"start": 905.26, "end": 906.26, "text": " enforces"}, {"start": 906.26, "end": 907.26, "text": " Bhagavata"}, {"start": 907.26, "end": 908.26, "text": " Dharma."}, {"start": 908.26, "end": 909.26, "text": " And,"}, {"start": 909.26, "end": 910.26, "text": " this way"}, {"start": 910.26, "end": 911.26, "text": " people"}, {"start": 911.26, "end": 912.26, "text": " become"}, {"start": 912.26, "end": 913.26, "text": " spiritually"}, {"start": 913.26, "end": 914.26, "text": " enlightened."}, {"start": 914.26, "end": 915.26, "text": " So,"}, {"start": 915.26, "end": 916.26, "text": " this"}, {"start": 916.26, "end": 917.26, "text": " is"}, {"start": 917.26, "end": 918.26, "text": " being"}, {"start": 918.26, "end": 919.26, "text": " mentioned"}, {"start": 919.26, "end": 920.26, "text": " by"}, {"start": 920.26, "end": 921.26, "text": " Yudhishthira"}, {"start": 921.26, "end": 922.26, "text": " Maharaj"}, {"start": 922.26, "end": 923.26, "text": " that all"}, {"start": 923.26, "end": 924.26, "text": " the"}, {"start": 924.26, "end": 925.26, "text": " forefathers"}, {"start": 925.26, "end": 926.26, "text": " of"}, {"start": 926.26, "end": 927.26, "text": " Yudhishthira"}, {"start": 927.26, "end": 928.26, "text": " Maharaj"}, {"start": 928.26, "end": 929.26, "text": " in"}, {"start": 929.26, "end": 930.26, "text": " this"}, {"start": 930.26, "end": 931.26, "text": " dynasty"}, {"start": 931.26, "end": 932.26, "text": " were"}, {"start": 932.26, "end": 933.26, "text": " all"}, {"start": 933.26, "end": 934.26, "text": " great"}, {"start": 934.26, "end": 935.26, "text": " personalities."}, {"start": 935.26, "end": 936.26, "text": " Now,"}, {"start": 936.26, "end": 937.26, "text": " will"}, {"start": 937.26, "end": 938.26, "text": " this"}, {"start": 938.26, "end": 939.26, "text": " child"}, {"start": 939.26, "end": 940.26, "text": " also"}, {"start": 940.26, "end": 941.26, "text": " be"}, {"start": 941.26, "end": 942.26, "text": " as"}, {"start": 942.26, "end": 943.26, "text": " great"}, {"start": 943.26, "end": 944.26, "text": " as"}, {"start": 944.26, "end": 945.26, "text": " those"}, {"start": 945.26, "end": 946.26, "text": " forefathers"}, {"start": 946.26, "end": 947.26, "text": " of our"}, {"start": 947.26, "end": 948.26, "text": " dynasty?"}, {"start": 948.26, "end": 949.26, "text": " That's"}, {"start": 949.26, "end": 950.26, "text": " the question"}, {"start": 950.26, "end": 951.26, "text": " he's"}, {"start": 951.26, "end": 952.26, "text": " asking."}, {"start": 952.26, "end": 953.26, "text": " I'll stop here."}]}